 is a list of all available theme files located in <strong>application\/views\/themes\/yourtheme\/views\/<\/strong> (views):<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>announcement.php &#8211; Single view announcement.<\/li>\n<li>announcements.php &#8211; List view announcements<\/li>\n<li>calendar.php &#8211; Customer calendar area<\/li>\n<li>company_profile.php &#8211; Company informations<\/li>\n<li>contractpdf.php &#8211; Contract PDF template<\/li>\n<li>contracts.php &#8211; List view contracts<\/li>\n<li>estimatehtml.php &#8211; Estimate HTML\u00a0template<\/li>\n<li>estimatepdf.php &#8211; Estimate PDF template<\/li>\n<li>files.php &#8211; Customer area for files to upload in the customer profile<\/li>\n<li>forgot_password.php &#8211; Customer forgot password template<\/li>\n<li>home.php &#8211; Customers dashboard after login<\/li>\n<li>invoicehtml.php &#8211; Invoice HTML\u00a0template<\/li>\n<li>invoicepdf.php &#8211; Invoice PDF template<\/li>\n<li>invoices.php &#8211; List view invoices<\/li>\n<li>knowledge_base.php &#8211; All knowledge base articles<\/li>\n<li>knowledge_base_article.php &#8211; Single knowledge base article<\/li>\n<li>login.php &#8211; Contact login template<\/li>\n<li>open_ticket.php &#8211; New ticket open template<\/li>\n<li>paymentpdf.php &#8211; Payment Receipt PDF template<\/li>\n<li>profile.php &#8211; Logged in contact profile<\/li>\n<li>project.php &#8211; Single project<\/li>\n<li>proposalpdf.php &#8211; Proposal PDF template<\/li>\n<li>proposals.php &#8211; List view proposals<\/li>\n<li>register.php &#8211; Contact\/Customer register template<\/li>\n<li>reset_password.php &#8211; Reset password template<\/li>\n<li>single_ticket.php &#8211; Contact view ticket template<\/li>\n<li>survey_view.php &#8211; Survey template<\/li>\n<li>tickets.php &#8211; List view tickets<\/li>\n<li>viewproposal.php &#8211; Proposal HTML template<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>If you want to change the client area look copy the existing main 